%p Dear #{h(@attendee.full_name)},

%p Your request for registration as part of group <strong>#{h(@group.name)}</strong> at #{@attendee.event.name} was received successfully.

- unless @attendee.courses.empty?
  %p Besides the conference, you also registered for the following courses:
  %ul
    - @attendee.courses.each do |course|
      %li '#{I18n.t(course.full_name)}'

%p Instructions to complete the registration process will be sent to your group organizer as soon the request for registration for all participants are received.

%h3 Important:

- deadline = @attendee.registration_date.to_date + 5
%p
  - unless @attendee.courses.empty?
    The payment confirmation for you group must be received until #{I18n.l(deadline)}. After that date, your place in the #{@attendee.courses.size > 1 ? 'courses' : 'course'} will no longer be ensured. To check place availability in any course, contact #{mail_to AppConfig[:organizer][:email]}.

%p If you have any questions, please contact us at #{mail_to AppConfig[:organizer][:email]}

%small [Please do not reply to this e-mail. It was sent from an unmonitored email address]